{"tid":1967954,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"肥媽為剛出世狗BB做人工呼吸：差啲以為救唔番","createTime":"2020-04-11T09:55:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T12:32:34.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"3847834ea7c4cbf182728eb697e3715c400d714a","tid":1967954,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T09:55:32.000Z","msg":"本身是愛狗之人的肥媽，昨日在社交平台宣佈家有喜事，她的愛犬SaSa誕下11隻狗BB，但其間發生了驚險事：「其實噚晚發生咗一啲小意外，就係同大家報喜後，11哥突然間出世，但佢一出世就冇呼吸，而SaSa都冇辦法幫佢，我都唔知點做，我當下只係希望人工呼吸能幫佢，但我不斷試，點整佢都唔郁。其實我原本冇打算同大家分享，因為我以為救唔番，都唔係咩開心的事，因為中間隔咗一個鐘頭都冇呼吸，但我真係唔想放棄，當我最後繼續做人工呼吸之後，我將佢攬住，用自己體溫畀佢，11哥突然奇蹟咳咗一下，我真係好感動好感動！」<br />\n<br />\n後來肥媽還說：「我真係當佢哋都係自己啲孫，都係生命去照顧，佢哋係我最好嘅親人，可能我未必所有步驟都做得啱，但感恩感恩，最後11哥可以救得番，最後11隻狗仔完完整整。」片中見到肥媽邊喊邊幫11哥做人工呼吸，有網民留言：「多謝阿媽冇放棄到隻狗仔，令我領悟到一個道理，即使身邊環境有幾差有幾無助，都唔好放棄，一定要堅持到最後，感恩。」接着有網民問肥媽會否全數收養？肥媽說：「我哋會留番4同11，其他我身邊的朋友要咗。」不過亦有人提議，最好方法還是幫狗狗絕育，肥媽則回覆：「其實一開始都係想幫佢絕育，但係人哋話狗女要嚟完第一次經期先可以做，跟住我有一個月唔喺香港，一睇唔實就咁。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200411/large/1586594084_a2b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200411%2Flarge%2F1586594084_a2b3.jpg&h=9efbd9c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200411/large/1586594085_44c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200411%2Flarge%2F1586594085_44c8.jpg&h=0d8b0979&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200411/large/1586594087_7335.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200411%2Flarge%2F1586594087_7335.jpg&h=ffbe95ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200411/large/1586594087_2228.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200411%2Flarge%2F1586594087_2228.jpg&h=ed555303&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200411/large/1586594087_a6d4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200411%2Flarge%2F1586594087_a6d4.jpg&h=530565ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200411/AUH3HWRC3XGSNSMRYBXYP6INS4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200411%2FAUH3HWRC3XGSNSMRYBXYP6INS4%2F&d=PwmYTnxQQ9jzt6ozq479VVe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=e5bd1c85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200411%2FAUH3HWRC3XGSNSMRYBXYP6INS4%2F&h=800fc792\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200411/AUH3HWRC3XGSNSMRYBXYP6INS4/</a>"},{"pid":"392605bf05972880fcde7a1ce1a21a36a21d5f8c","tid":1967954,"uid":65429,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T10:02:57.000Z","msg":"人美心善"},{"pid":"4c7d0fba62ed79bd894c2f3992b67c80f29835e3","tid":1967954,"uid":261773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T10:11:18.000Z","msg":"睇標題以為係果啲狗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d453ebf8f2dfacc373e469dc34174189191da6c","tid":1967954,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T10:11:32.000Z","msg":"11哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3529b8f605ed7a96c48dc97930616d6f9abab382","tid":1967954,"uid":40570,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T10:15:35.000Z","msg":"ICU確診警長有救了"},{"pid":"25b832c0acc1bafdaad1c80eebcbf28ae8e1a5dc","tid":1967954,"uid":189109,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T10:15:56.000Z","msg":"隻狗寧願自己救唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"